query_transparent
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_transparent

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_transparent -  This method returns the current transparent value of the object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_transparent()
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if the object is transparent

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/close_lock.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the current transparent
value of the object.
A transparent object is one in which you can see the
inventory even if it is closed.  This is also
used for light propogration.

.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
reset_transparent(), query_transparent()
.EP

